1. Edit xecjksetpunct-main.tex to set the ghostscript executable and fonts .

2. for texlive
      xelatex --shell-escape xecjksetpunct-main

   for miktex, run
      xelatex --enable-write18 xecjksetpunct-main

3. move  xeCJK.cfg  to the directory $TEXMFLOCAL/tex/xelatex/xeCJK

4. run texhash 